{"word":"ἀνάθημα","slug":"ἀνάθημα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάθημα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀνατίθημι, ἀνάθεμα.</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a votive offering set up</i> in a temple, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a delight, ornament</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}